name: Jasmijn Van Koningsbruggen
summary:
Finished my Master of Science in Business Administration last June and currently focussing on finishing my Master of Science in Finance, which I am planning on finishing this December. From January 2023 on I will be looking for a new job in the field of Corporate Strategy or Corporate Finance. I have interest in consultancy, oriented towards (international) corporate expansions and Sustainability. However, I am interested to learn about other Finance or MBA related functions.

Besides studying I work at a restaurant two times a week. This job was perfect to combine with studying. I got many responsibilities and at the same time I could be around people all the time, which I like. Next to that, I enjoy travelling and exploring new places. Also, I love to play field hockey, which I have done for a substantial part of my life. Besides, I have been busy organising different events for the student association I am a member of (+2000 people).

name: Stella Ravesteijn
summary: Na het VWO gestart met de Bachelor Economie en Bedrijfskunde aan de UvA richting Accounting en Control. Na de Bachelor, de Master Accounting and Conrol (richting Accounting) aan de UvA afgerond. Per 1 september 2017 gestart als Staff op de Regio Audit van Deloitte. Per oktober 2019 de opleiding tot theoretisch Register Accountant (RA) aan de UvA succesvol afgerond en per 2021 kunnen doorgroeien naar de functie Junior Manager. In deze functie bediende ik zowel private als publieke klanten. Vanaf begin 2022 ben ik werkzaam bij BMC waarbij ik gedetacheerd ben bij diverse publieke (gemeentelijke) klanten. Hierbij vervul ik, afhankelijk van de opdracht, verschillende rollen binnen concern control (VIC) en financiën.
